<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Durance" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Durance,</orth> imprisonment: <cit><quote>perpetual d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 3.1.67" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. III, 1, 67</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>set thee from d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 3.130" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL III, 130</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>is now in d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tn 5.283" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. V, 283</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.5.36" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B V, 5, 36</bibl>. Quibbling: <cit><quote>gives them suits of d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 4.3.27" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. IV, 3, 27</bibl></cit> (the dress worn in prisons, and a lasting dress). <cit><quote>is not a buff jerkin a most sweet robe of d.?</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.2.49" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 2, 49</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>